---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Contact from '../components/Contact.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Experience — Jinit Shah"
  description="Work experience and projects of Jinit Shah: Manhattan Associates, GYD (Graph Your Data), Ventera, Deep Cognition, Renee, and more."
  current="/experience"
  headerOn="dark"
>
  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split entry" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>Senior Software Engineer</h3>
        <p>Manhattan Associates <em>(June 2023 - Present)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Spearheading AI adoption across the department: implemented AI pipelines using agents,
            reusable skills, and agentic workflows to improve internal developer tooling, enabling
            faster and more reliable software delivery.
          </li>
          <li>
            Designed, built, deployed, and maintained Apache Camel integration server in a
            microservices architecture, improving system interoperability and reducing data
            transfer latency by 60%.
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed and maintained multiple full stack applications across large-scale, FedRAMP
            authorized supply chain and warehouse management platforms serving FEMA and DeCA,
            processing millions of transactions.
          </li>
          <li>
            Led an internal project to create an environment calendar web application to track
            server statuses, enhancing visibility and operational efficiency.
          </li>
          <li>Developed PL/SQL scripts to edit relational DBs.</li>
          <li>
            Upgraded and installed Software AG’s MyWebMethods and Integration server to streamline
            and unify our system architecture.
          </li>
          <li class="tech-list">
            Angular - Java - Python - Spring - Apache Camel - SQL - AWS - GCP - Terraform - Ansible
            - Docker - Kubernetes - Jenkins - LangChain - Agentic Workflows - Microservices
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split entry" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>GYD (Graph Your Data)</h3>
        <p><em>Pronounced: Guide</em></p>
        <p>Virginia Tech <em>(Spring 2023)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>
            GYD is a webapp that can converts text-based information into visual representations of
            it using a knowledge graph, summary and a chat box.
          </li>
          <li>
            It summarizes long texts with a bi-directional LSTM RNN model (accuracy: 0.96) and an
            additional backup Pegasus LLM.
          </li>
          <li>
            For generating answers to user questions, we fine-tuned a BERT LLM using SQuaD 2.0
            database (accuracy 0.93).
          </li>
          <li>
            GYD reduces bias in information processing and enables users to understand information
            through its relationships, rather than through a linear text flow.
          </li>
          <li class="tech-list">
            Machine Learning - RNN - LLM - Angular - NodeJS - ExpressJS - HTML - CSS - Google Cloud
            Platform
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split entry" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>Software Engineering Intern</h3>
        <p>Ventera Corporation <em>(Summer 2022)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Developed recommendation ML models for a web application that helps users pick restaurants.</li>
          <li>
            Helped design and develop the front-end, back-end and server side for that web
            application that helps users pick what restaurant to pick based on various filters.
          </li>
          <li>Developed guidelines for human-centered AI, focusing on ethics and bias mitigation.</li>
          <li class="tech-list">
            K-means - Python - Anaconda - JavaScript - Angular - NodeJS - ExpressJS - HTML - CSS -
            MySQL
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split entry" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>Machine Learning Intern</h3>
        <p>Deep Cognition <em>(Nov 2020 - May 2021)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Developed CNN, RNN and various ML models</li>
          <li>Created tutorials for new members to make ML models on Deep Learning Studio</li>
          <li class="tech-list">CNN - RNN - LSTM - Python - Anaconda - Deep Learning Studio</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split entry" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>Founder &amp; CEO</h3>
        <p>Renee <em>(May 2021 - Present)</em></p>
        <p><em>Code snippets available on request</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Non-profit aimed at helping make the world a better place with the power of ML and CS!</li>
          <li>
            Developed Handsway which is a one-of-a-kind app that translates ASL signs into text in
            real time.
          </li>
          <li>
            Also solely coded another social media app from scratch and built a fully functional
            social media with an elegant frontend, powerful backend, and secure server side
            functions and incorporated features including messaging, posting pictures and texts,
            getting notifications, setting up profiles and posts as public or private and most
            importantly 3D and 2D visualizations for a new type of posts.
          </li>
          <li class="tech-list">
            Swift - SwiftUI - JavaScript - Firebase - Xcode - Android Studio Manager - Full Stack
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split entry" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>IT Intern</h3>
        <p>Linc Solutions <em>(Summer 2018, 2019)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Helped me understand computers inside out</li>
          <li>Hardware and networking, Software installation and configuration, System update</li>
          <li>
            Troubleshooting and fixing wide variety of broken electronics including laptops,
            tablets, desktops, switches etc
          </li>
          <li class="tech-list">Hardware - Networking - Troubleshooting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split entry" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>Web Designer</h3>
        <p>Happiness Yoga <em>(Summer 2018)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Designed and handled
            <a href="https://www.happinessyoga.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">website</a> for a
            local yoga business. Incorporated payment systems, scheduling and promotions
          </li>
          <li>
            Created and managed social media accounts. Advertised and promoted the business using
            various marketing strategies
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Contact />
</Base>
